      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly representing a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless, maintaining a deep, factory-perfect shine with no scratches, chips, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather that looks and feels brand new and every electronic component functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved car that has clearly been garage-kept and pampered since day one.",
